<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Um, I don't know why.

32
00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:48.259
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: And so I am interested here, because I know that the director did something a little different with this one, I think I've heard, right?

33
00:02:48.740 --> 00:02:50.479
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Okay, nope.

34
00:02:50.479 --> 00:02:51.740
