00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:19.740
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: And so every few years you knew that you were going to go into the theatre.

216
00:13:19.740 --> 00:13:24.480
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: And I feel like the majority of the series that are being made today are superhero.

217
00:13:24.480 --> 00:13:28.559
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: So if you're not into superheroes, Trug, you know?

218
00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:32.840
<v 9C192306-9A0E-4483-99EF-8228817ABFFE>Al: Yeah, okay, so there's a lot in that, right?

219
00:13:32.500 --> 00:13:34.240
