00:13:50.720 --> 00:14:09.379
<v 9C192306-9A0E-4483-99EF-8228817ABFFE>Al: Now, granted, the total amount of money, the box office makes per year is down on 2019 and the 10 years before that, roughly, um, because obviously COVID massive problem.

224
00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:51.502
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Mm-hmm.

225
00:14:04.500 --> 00:14:05.002
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Yeah.

226
00:14:08.500 --> 00:14:09.002
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Yeah.

227
00:14:09.379 --> 00:14:16.279
<v 9C192306-9A0E-4483-99EF-8228817ABFFE>Al: But I don't think it's as simple as any, as saying it's because of COVID or it's because of bad films or anything like that.

228
00:14:16.279 --> 00:14:20.480
<v 9C192306-9A0E-4483-99EF-8228817ABFFE>Al: Because like generally it's been going up since COVID as well.

