00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:09.980
<v 9C192306-9A0E-4483-99EF-8228817ABFFE>Al: Yeah, but they make a lot of money.

241
00:15:08.320 --> 00:15:09.159
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: So.

242
00:15:09.519 --> 00:15:12.639
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Yeah, I'm sure, well, and they're going to make,

243
00:15:09.980 --> 00:15:11.480
<v 9C192306-9A0E-4483-99EF-8228817ABFFE>Al: Right?

