01:13:52.220 --> 01:13:55.579
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Usually like the, again, the, there's that three-part body plan.

1227
01:13:55.579 --> 01:13:57.439
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: They have 3 pairs of legs.

