<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: And then antennae or how they sense and smell and taste in all of that, taste their environment.

1236
01:15:00.619 --> 01:15:07.579
<v A7BCC9D0-ED51-4B67-9AE7-4017FAECDA7E>Codey: Um, that's their antennae and their eyes are like the 2 main sensory organs that insects have.

